; Photo, Winning is never tiring, says Kevin Crow, the MISL's defender of the 
year the past two seasons. VINCE COMPAGNONE / Los Angeles Times; Photo, The 
Sockers' Victor Nogueira emerged as the league's top goalie during '88-'89 
season. STAN HONDA / For The Times 
