LOAN FRAUD; MISMANAGEMENT; GOVERNMENT MISCONDUCT; LOANS; PIERCE, SAMUEL R JR; 
FIFTH AMENDMENT; UNITED STATES -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS 
</P>
