</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
ENGLAND -- GOVERNMENT; ENGLAND -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; RESIGNATIONS; ENGLAND 
-- ECONOMY; ENGLAND -- POLITICS; THATCHER, MARGARET; LAWSON, NIGEL; MAJOR, 
JOHN; WALTERS, ALAN; EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES; GATES, ROBERT 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
