better English pronunciation at the Hunt Branch Library. RICK PERRY / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, Student Joy Piper, right, attempts a difficult word in 
the Fullerton class, while Gloria Rocha watches. ; Photo, Josef Mair and Dora 
Harrigan study pronunciation at their home. ROBERT LACHMAN / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
